<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="18" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="17.[151,1437,152,898]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
ETYMOLOGY. This new species is named after E. Grobbelaar (
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34248" box="[958,1042,632,658]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34248" name="Agricultural Research Council-Plant Protection Research Institute" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">SANC</collectionCode>
), one of its collectors, in recognition of her kind and valuable collaboration.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
